{"data":{"post":{"id":"ec09f649-0938-58a5-87fe-9be33ddc31d1","html":"<p>感谢贝贝提供的插画(植物大战僵尸 · 系列2)\n\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/3b0fe073a51a47f48ec9a772d987877d/a11c5/plantsvszombies.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"plantsvszombies\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/3b0fe073a51a47f48ec9a772d987877d/78f2b/plantsvszombies.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/3b0fe073a51a47f48ec9a772d987877d/dce19/plantsvszombies.jpg 200w,\n/static/3b0fe073a51a47f48ec9a772d987877d/c1413/plantsvszombies.jpg 400w,\n/static/3b0fe073a51a47f48ec9a772d987877d/78f2b/plantsvszombies.jpg 800w,\n/static/3b0fe073a51a47f48ec9a772d987877d/ab4c4/plantsvszombies.jpg 1200w,\n/static/3b0fe073a51a47f48ec9a772d987877d/bc99b/plantsvszombies.jpg 1600w,\n/static/3b0fe073a51a47f48ec9a772d987877d/a11c5/plantsvszombies.jpg 2016w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    \n<br>\n记得曾经看过一部科幻片《逃离克隆岛》，故事从电影中人物开始思考: 为何他脑海里有类此想法?由此，故事引入……<br>\n</p>\n<h3>你是否想过：你是怎么思考的？</h3>\n<h4>场景1：</h4>\n<p>当你的boss来询问：昨天的任务进展怎样？什么时候能完成？<br>\n你的第一反应是啥？<br>\n<em>天天催，天天催，催魂啊……</em><br>\n<br>\n<em>昨天已经汇报了，为啥今天还问？存在风险吗？</em><br>\n<br>\n<em>老大事必躬亲，太尽职了……</em><br>\n<br>\n……<br>\n<em>我得想一个办法，让他看到进展，让他安心……</em><br>\n</p>\n<h3>有没有想过：你为什么会这么思考？</h3>\n<h4>场景2:</h4>\n<p>周末在家吃饭<br>\nA：谁洗碗?<br>\nB:“石头剪刀布”决定<br>\nA/B：成交~<br>\nB：哈哈，这么好的表现机会，非要跟我玩“石头剪刀布”，愿赌服输，你洗碗哦~<br>\nA：好，我等下就去洗。<br>\n<br>\n半小时过去了~~~<br>\nB：怎么还没洗碗啊，说话要算数啊。<br>\nA：今天周末，让我休息一下。<br>\nB：啥？不是你教我“执行力”的么？怎么只许州官放火不许百姓点灯啊……<br>\n……<br>\n</p>\n<h4>这些生活的剪影，折射了我们的“思维方式”。也许你并未发现：凡是以自我为中心；也许你没有察觉：其实，你常常“顾影自怜”。</h4>\n<h4>平凡的人，可能无法达到圣人的公平、公正对待每件事。</h4>\n<h3>“已所不与勿施于人”，可以来引导我们的思维方式、行为处事。</h3>","fields":{"slug":"/2018-12-10/mode-of-think/","prefix":"2018-12-10"},"frontmatter":{"title":"mode of thinking","author":"文:Jane 图(植物大战僵尸 · 系列2):贝贝","category":"thought","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"resize":{"src":"/static/3b0fe073a51a47f48ec9a772d987877d/ada8c/plantsvszombies.jpg"}}}}},"authornote":{"id":"e6ec6ad4-4c6b-586c-bfdf-8cdf2d09548f","html":"<p>hustlrb<br>\n<br>\n明德厚学 求是创新</p>"},"site":{"siteMetadata":{"facebook":{"appId":""}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2018-12-10/mode-of-think/","prev":{"id":"98fc8a79-7ba1-54ba-93e3-324cc485f15d","fields":{"slug":"/2018-11-30/swimming/","prefix":"2018-11-30","source":"posts"},"frontmatter":{"title":"swimming learning(1)","category":"swimming"}},"next":{"id":"0f6f51ee-2a84-5afe-bb96-8dbf4b2bcf6d","fields":{"slug":"/2018-12-11/excessive-interoperability/","prefix":"2018-12-11","source":"posts"},"frontmatter":{"title":"过度协助","category":"thought"}},"source":"posts"}}